item.title: CVE-2009-4267|2024-08-07T06:54:10.235Z -- apache%20software%20foundation -- juddi
item.description: The console in Apache jUDDI 3.0.0 does not properly escape line feeds, which allows remote authenticated users to spoof log entries via the numRows parameter.
